https://image.tmdb.org/t/p/w500/h9VE3zKFn2ZCYQLFKasaQwOjUPq.jpg Anaheim's House of Blues sets the stage for this reunion concert featuring Southern California natives the Adolescents, the groundbreaking Orange County band known for helping to spearhead the punk revival of the 1980s. The set list includes "Kids of the Black Hole," "Amoeba," "Self-Destruct," "Democracy," "L.A. Girl," "Things Start Moving," "American Lockdown," "Within These Walls," "Welcome to Reality" and "Word Attack." Adolescents: Live at the House of Blues
